Usage: report_cell_stack_area [-help] [-cell <string>] [-file <string>]
                              [-group <string>]

-help              # Prints out the command usage
-cell <string>     # specify the cell(s) that needs to report
                   # (string, optional)
-file <string>     # The reported information is dumped into the specified file
                   # (string, optional)
-group <string>    # specify the group(s) that needs to report
                   # (string, optional)